</title>
<subSubSection id="BA3519FFA299C83208C7B444C83CCA41" pageId="null" pageNumber="134" type="description">
<paragraph id="174A01EA21A7586BC204DAEEB7EB0D33" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">
10-30 cm hoch. Stengel besonders im obern Teil dicht behaart (
<emphasis id="F308D6F5B49EEC462979FD2645E1A731" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">Haare dort 1,5</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="04AC0C2EBCCF0437FCF4A059CB6E0444" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">3 mm lang</emphasis>
). 
<emphasis id="49A2BA13C1735F48A201C4B6F116C2D3" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">
<normalizedToken id="A0E66EBAE3ED094B9F517FA8B48A016E" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
beiderseits dicht und wollig behaart.
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="959F974D09AAB9A12B54038BB48901B0" originalValue="Stengelblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">Stengelblaetter</normalizedToken>
am Grunde 
<normalizedToken id="76A7E0418A6AA3AEDE42A62F82EFE290" originalValue="herzförmig" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">herzfoermig</normalizedToken>
. 
<emphasis id="23D773EB8EE50E86552265D6AE956CAE" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">Kelch 12</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="6D59914F11028577FA94E2BD0FE8EB76" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">15 mm lang</emphasis>
, mit 4-5,5 mm langen, sich 
<normalizedToken id="7C528F529C2137633970C16CA434D624" originalValue="allmählich" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">allmaehlich</normalizedToken>
in die Granne 
<normalizedToken id="7FA502A881332722147FF053ED1D9BFA" originalValue="verschmälernden" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">verschmaelernden</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="C2A7672D2F8F23557DDA59705AC83F42" originalValue="Zähnen" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">Zaehnen</normalizedToken>
, im untern Teil kahl. 
<emphasis id="66F55F7EC8CA1869CFB11F05C0A08AE5" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">Krone 15</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="35D857F9D30733A97795A09F35BC96B1" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">22 mm lang.</emphasis>
- 
<normalizedToken id="60E01C8F22757AA53C7D2BF20B59FE97" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="9499BAF5B005EE55871C6B44B4EFA97E" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">
<emphasis id="7393DD2D18760DA9BB4B597196BE3C70" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="6B13A279EC4B8F810095C1CBB0FC5F45" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">16:</emphasis>
Material aus botanischen 
<normalizedToken id="D62ADF22CE607830CF31185106E3C802" originalValue="Gärten" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">Gaerten</normalizedToken>
(Lang 1940).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8F1395AF9C05430F35EAC50072549AA3" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">
<emphasis id="61FD6E7A7EF4B4BF14CBD34B4DDA0AFF" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">Standort.</emphasis>
Subalpin (selten alpin). Trockene 
<normalizedToken id="4FB7ECB0D6890F20779354EA002856EB" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">Boeden</normalizedToken>
. Magere Wiesen, 
<normalizedToken id="31DF22355B02CC16D23CAD90FD701EF1" originalValue="Zwergstrauchgebüsche" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">Zwergstrauchgebuesche</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="1D82AE01BAB1B8AB211B6B4B442CDC1B" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">
<emphasis id="D456E2D836704623D56C457CB431B1B7" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">
Verbreitung. Mittel- und 
<normalizedToken id="AFF40E816FBC2B0D064F5ACBE029221C" originalValue="südeuropäische" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">suedeuropaeische</normalizedToken>
Gebirgspflanze
</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="B5C6FBE4B043FA739576CC7022CB3DC1" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">westlich</emphasis>
): Nordspanische Gebirge, 
<normalizedToken id="ED86F4A76FCD2BA0D62963BED26ABC42" originalValue="Pyrenäen" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">Pyrenaeen</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="A788B932C2CC2930CC4804CC66BE0F14" originalValue="Südalpen" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">Suedalpen</normalizedToken>
, Apennin, Abruzzen. - Im Gebiet: Westalpen (
<normalizedToken id="1B252039A8FC6258486E4F9545F4E610" originalValue="ostwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">ostwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis Dora Baltea, Val de Bagne, 
<normalizedToken id="A9035133E8DD059DFD7AF70FB767CE0F" originalValue="Lötschental" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">Loetschental</normalizedToken>
, Simmental und 
<normalizedToken id="181CD75741F500642AFB03EE2B9B8A40" originalValue="Südalpen" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">Suedalpen</normalizedToken>
(Anzasca im Valle 
<normalizedToken id="57AB1D0F451A1B189F5B6F20A25688F6" originalValue="d’Ossola" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">d'Ossola</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="AB7339F20F378DCDA3C93E4A78E65D11" originalValue="südliches" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">suedliches</normalizedToken>
Misox, 
<normalizedToken id="AAFD5FB27858359CDB2B92AF54007544" originalValue="Camoghè" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">Camoghe</normalizedToken>
, Kette der Denti della Vecchia, Grigna, Bergamasker Alpen); nicht 
<normalizedToken id="27C49CA405D9A7213CA9E96829C462D7" originalValue="häufig" pageId="null" pageNumber="134">haeufig</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
